title: Watch: Guy Tries to Race Horses, Definitely Pulls a Hammie
text:
Watch: Guy Tries to Race Horses, Definitely Pulls a Hammie When you race a horse, you should probably stretch first. By Kit Fox   5:17 pm This punter showed a nice turn of foot before pulling up lame in the last at Hobart on Sunday… pic.twitter.com/Oe7OOrPsXx 
— Sky Racing (@SkyRacingAU) January 25, 2017 
An ambitious human tried to outrun a pack of thoroughbreds at a racetrack in Australia last week. It did not end well. Advertisement
